args: The hell's gotten into everyone lately?\nThey act like this cheerleadin' crap is the\ngreatest thing since a pork-fat sandwich!
It takes way more than yellin' dumb\nrhymes in yer face to solve problems!
I mean, yeah, I suppose maybe it does\nSOMETHIN', but it sure as hell ain't the\nmiracle everybody's sayin' it is!
Aw, Ranzal! Do you really think that?!\n*sniff* That hurts.
H-hey! I never woulda said all that if I\nknew ya was standin' RIGHT THERE!
Look, all I'm sayin' is that encouragin'\nwords ain't exactly gonna defeat the\nEmpire and bring about world peace.
Hmph! Very well, sir. It seems you\nleave me with no other option.
Don't think I like where this is headed...
I can make ANYONE a believer in the\npower of cheer—including you!

So starting tomorrow, you will be
attending Emma's Cheer Camp!
I'm gonna spend THE ENTIRE DAY
following you and cheering you on!
Er, but I suppose ya earned a day what\nwith all the work ya been doin' here...\nOkay, kid—show ol' Ranzal what ya got!
I'm gonna make you a true believer!
*yawn* Oh man, where's the coffee?\nI gotta get... Uh, Emma? The hell ya—
RANZAL, RANZAL, YOU'RE NOT DEAD!\nSO GET UP OUT OF THAT STINKY BED!
Beat it, kid! I'm a grown man—I don't\nneed help gettin' outta my own damn bed!
But I bet you dooooo need...this special\nbreakfast I made JUST FOR YOU! Yaaay!
*sniff* Oh man, is that fresh-baked bread?\nDamn, it looks delicious! *chomp* *horf*

All right then! Now that you've eaten,
it's time to start the rest of your morning...
GO, RANZAL, GO! SEIZE THAT DAY!
TAKE A BIG STEP OUTTA THE DOORWAY!
Huh. Yeah, okay. This ain't terrible—but\nit ALSO ain't makin' my socks roll up and\ndown like everybody said it would!
Holy snot, you nearly decapitated me with\nthat axe swing! Talk about AWESOME!
LET'S GO, RANZAL! SWING THAT AXE!\nJUST TRY NOT TO PUT IT IN OUR BACKS!
Ya really ain't gonna give up on this,\nare ya, kid? Well then...HAAAAAH!
Ohmigosh, Ranzal, that was AMAZING!\nYou're the best. For seriously.
Heh. I could maybe get used to this...
I mean, no! Hell no! It'll take more'n a\nfew honeyed words to sway Ranzal!
(Time to see what this kid's\nreally made of...)
Um, Ranzal? Is your training over?\nWhat are you doing?
I always take a nap after I've done\nmy day's trainin'. Night!
(Bwa ha ha! NOW I got her! She can't\nsay boo for fear of wakin' me—which\nmeans she can't cheer me on, neither!)
Nighty niiiiight... Sleep so tiiiiight...\nWatch out for the bedfiend's biiiite... ♪
(A lullaby? Damn. Didn't see that comin'.)
(Hell, she's actually good at this.\nThink I'm gonna...nod off for real...)
This is rougher than I... The hell?!
GO, RANZAL, GO! KILL THAT THING!\nTAKE ITS HEAD WITH A BIG AXE SWING!
Get outta here, kid! It's dangerous!
I told you, Emma's Cheer Camp lasts for\nan entire day—and the day is NOT over!
Stop, ya dope! They got a nest over there!
Oh, really? Then off I gooooo!
Oh, for the love'a... Hold on! I'm comin'!
N-no! It's fine! I've totally got this!
Just take 'em out while they're all\nsuper distracted trying to kill me!
Don't worry about me! *pant*\nI'll help however I can! *dodge*
GO, GO, RANZAL! WIN THE DAY!\nDON'T LET 'EM EAT ME AND STUFF, OKAY?!
This kid's gonna die, and yet all she\ncan do is keep cheerin' me on!
And it's all because you beat that fiend\nfaster than you normally would have.
Looks like Emma's Cheer Camp\nwas a smashing success.
Shut up about yer damn cheer camp!
The only reason I beat it faster than usual\nis 'cause you were gonna DIE if I didn't!
See?! It DID work! So do you\nbelieve me now or what?
Would ya listen to me for one...\nAh, hell. Sure, kid. It worked.
Hee! I'm so happy to hear...that...\nAnd so...sleepy... Zzzzzz...
Still, I think I get it now—that cheerin'\nthing is more than just hot air.
Ya win this round, Emma.\nCheer camp worked like a charm.
